n = int(input())
    A = list(map(int, input().split()))
    m = int(input())
    B = list(map(int, input().split()))
    A.sort()
    B.sort()
    A = A[::-1]
    B = B[::-1]
    for i in range(n):
        for j in range(m):
            if A[i] == B[j]:
                print(A[i])
                break
